    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<p>Drowned wolves are risen undead wolves, product of the Rot's spread through Svellheim's bone-fields and frozen waterways. Waterlogged fur clings to skeletal frames, and bioluminescent ichor seeps from wounds, leaving faint trails in darkness. They navigate entirely by sound and scent — Blind Hunting makes them immune to blindness and sight-based concealment. In water or soggy ground they gain enhanced speed, and their sharp Bite slows targets while their Lunge can knock prey prone.</p>",
        "public": ""
